=================================
 Czech Named Entities Corpus 2.0
=================================

Czech Named Entity Corpus is a corpus of 8993 Czech sentences with manually
annotated 35220 Czech named entities, classified according to a
two-level hierarchy of 46 named entities. Further documentation of the corpus
is available in doc subdirectory.

