Corpus Structure
================

--- data
        --- plain       Czech named entities manual annotations in plain text format
        --- xml_simple  Czech named entities in simple xml, without morphologic analysis
        --- treex       Czech named entities in treex format (xml), with morphologic analysis
        --- html        Czech named entities in html format with highlighted named entities
--- doc                 Documentation
--- tools
        --- namedent_annotations_to_html.pl       Convert plain -> html format
        --- namedent_annotations_to_xml_simple.pl Convert plain -> xml format
        --- Treex/Block/Read/CNEC.pm              Convert plain -> treex format
        --- statistics.pl                         Compute statistics of corpus in plain format
        --- compare_ne_outputs_v3.pl              Evaluate NER output on CNEC

See http://ufal.mff.cuni.cz/treex/ for more about Treex.


Publications and Documentation
==============================

The doc folder contains the description of the corpus, mainly in doc.pdf.
Moreover, the annotation process for this corpus is described in these
publications:

  Ševčíková, M., Žabokrtský, Z., Krůza, O.: Zpracování pojmenovaných entit
  v českých textech. Technical Report TR-2007-36 (2007) -- part of this release
  in doc/techrep-ne-2007.pdf

  Ševčíková, M., Žabokrtský, Z., Krůza, O.: Named entities in czech: Annotating
  data and developing NE tagger. In: Matoušek, V., Mautner, P. (eds.) TSD 2007.
  LNCS (LNAI), vol. 4629, pp. 188–195. Springer, Heidelberg (2007)

The published work about this corpus further includes:

  Kravalová, J., Žabokrtský, Z.: Czech named entity corpus and SVM-based
  recognizer. In: Proceedings of the 2009 Named Entities Workshop: Shared Task on
  Transliteration. NEWS 2009, pp. 194–201. Association for Computational
  Linguistics (2009)

  Konkol, M., Konopík, M.: Maximum Entropy Named Entity Recognition for Czech
  Language. In: Habernal, I., Matoušek, V. (eds.) TSD 2011. LNCS, vol. 6836, pp.
  203–210. Springer, Heidelberg (2011)

  Straková, J., Straka, M., Hajič, J.: A New State-of-The-Art Czech Named Entity
  Recognizer. In: Habernal, I., Matoušek, V. (eds.) TSD 2013. LNCS, vol. 8082,
  pp. 68-75

  Konkol, M., Konopík, M.: CRF-based Czech Named Entity Recognizer and
  Consolidation of Czech NER Research. In: Habernal, I., Matoušek, V. (eds.) TSD
  2013. LNCS, vol. 8082, pp. 153-160
